data.description: *****Price Improvement****Well-maintained 3 level end-unit townhome that features wall to wall carpet, CAC,  assigned parking, living room, dining area, kitchen and powder room on 1st level; 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths on 2nd level; and finished basement, 1/2 bath on walkout basement level.  The property has a level rear yard for those summer cook-outs.  There is easy access to the Metro and interstate 495 for commuting to DC, VA, and Baltimore. and close proximity to shopping and entertainment.
